#

Spicy Tuna Toast

10 min
$8.5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

fishglutensoy

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinlow-carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

easyquickhealthyspicy

Description

A quick and flavorful dish featuring fresh tuna on crispy toast with a spicy kick.

Ingredients

  • canned tuna (in water): 1 can (5 oz)
  • sriracha sauce: 1 tablespoon
  • mayonnaise: 2 tablespoons
  • green onions: 2, chopped
  • bread (sourdough or whole grain): 2 slices
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
